# 测试账号密码
# 管理员： admin Admin@123
# 普通用户： user1 User1@123

### 登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user1",
  "password": "User1@123"
}

### 获取用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取仪表盘数据
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 获取权限列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 获取用户列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/test/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
